<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kasaysayan ng Pilipinas | Philippine History</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --phil-blue: #0038A8;
            --phil-red: #CE1126;
            --phil-gold: #FCD116;
            --dark: #1a1a2e;
            --light: #f5f5f0;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--light);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated Background */
        .bg-animation {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .sun-rays {
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, transparent 0deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 20deg, transparent 40deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 60deg, transparent 80deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 100deg, transparent 120deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 140deg, transparent 160deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 180deg, transparent 200deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 220deg, transparent 240deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 260deg, transparent 280deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 300deg, transparent 320deg, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.03) 340deg, transparent 360deg);
            animation: rotate 60s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.5rem 5%;
            background: rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--phil-gold), #fff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--light);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--phil-gold);
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-content {
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem);
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--phil-gold) 50%, #fff 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shimmer {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        .hero-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 3rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 2rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
            40% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px); }
            60% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px); }
        }

        .scroll-indicator::before {
            content: '↓';
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--phil-gold);
        }

        /* Timeline Section */
        .timeline-section {
            padding: 6rem 5%;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 25%;
            width: 50%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--phil-gold), transparent);
        }

        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 2px;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--phil-blue), var(--phil-red));
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(50px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease;
        }

        .timeline-item.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .timeline-content {
            width: 45%;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .timeline-content:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.1);
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-left: 0;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .timeline-date {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--phil-gold);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: var(--phil-gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 4px solid var(--dark);
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.5);
        }

        /* Era Cards */
        .eras-section {
            padding: 6rem 5%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .eras-grid {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .era-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 56, 168, 0.2), rgba(206, 17, 38, 0.2));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.4s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .era-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent, rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.1));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s;
        }

        .era-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .era-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--phil-gold);
        }

        .era-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .era-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--phil-gold);
        }

        .era-period {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .era-desc {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        /* Heroes Section */
        .heroes-section {
            padding: 6rem 5%;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .heroes-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .hero-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--phil-blue), var(--phil-red));
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .hero-card:hover::after {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .hero-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .hero-name {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--phil-gold);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .hero-role {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Footer with Developers */
        footer {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 4rem 5% 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(252, 209, 22, 0.2);
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .developers {
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .dev-title {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .dev-names {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--phil-gold), #fff, var(--phil-gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .dev-tagline {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .footer-quote {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            font-style: italic;
            position: relative;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .footer-quote::before,
        .footer-quote::after {
            content: '"';
            font-size: 4rem;
            position: absolute;
            color: var(--phil-gold);
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .footer-quote::before {
            top: -20px;
            left: 0;
        }

        .footer-quote::after {
            bottom: -40px;
            right: 0;
        }

        .copyright {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .timeline::before {
                left: 20px;
            }

            .timeline-item {
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }

            .timeline-content {
                width: calc(100% - 60px);
                margin-left: 40px !important;
                text-align: left !important;
            }

            .timeline-dot {
                left: 20px;
            }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
        }

        /* Loading Animation */
        .loader {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--dark);
            z-index: 9999;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
        }

        .loader.hidden {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .loader-sun {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: var(--phil-gold);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px var(--phil-gold);
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Loader -->
    <div class="loader" id="loader">
        <div class="loader-sun"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Background Animation -->
    <div class="bg-animation">
        <div class="sun-rays"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="logo">KASAYSAYAN</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#timeline">Timeline</a></li>
                <li><a href="#eras">Eras</a></li>
                <li><a href="#heroes">Heroes</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>The Philippine<br>Chronicles</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">A Journey Through Time</p>
            <p class="hero-description">
                Discover the rich tapestry of Philippine history—from ancient kingdoms and Spanish colonization 
                to revolution, independence, and the modern republic. A story of resilience, courage, and unwavering 
                spirit.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Timeline Section -->
    <section class="timeline-section" id="timeline">
        <h2 class="section-title">Historical Timeline</h2>
        
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1521</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Magellan's Arrival</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Ferdinand Magellan arrives in the Philippines, marking the first European contact. 
                        He is killed in the Battle of Mactan by Lapu-Lapu's warriors.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1565-1815</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">The Galleon Trade</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Spanish colonization begins. The Manila-Acapulco galleon trade flourishes, 
                        connecting Asia with the Americas for 250 years.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1872</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Gomburza Execution</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Fathers Mariano Gomez, Jose Burgos, and Jacinto Zamora are executed by the Spaniards, 
                        sparking revolutionary sentiments among Filipinos.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1892</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">La Liga Filipina</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        José Rizal founds the civic organization La Liga Filipina, advocating for peaceful reform. 
                        Andrés Bonifacio later establishes the Katipunan.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1896</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Cry of Pugadlawin</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Katipuneros tear their cedulas in defiance of Spanish rule, marking the beginning of 
                        the Philippine Revolution.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1898</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Declaration of Independence</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        General Emilio Aguinaldo proclaims Philippine independence from Spain in Kawit, Cavite. 
                        The first Philippine flag is unfurled and the national anthem is played.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1899-1902</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Philippine-American War</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Conflict erupts between Filipino revolutionaries and U.S. forces following the 
                        Treaty of Paris which ceded the Philippines to America for $20 million.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1935</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Commonwealth Era</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        The Philippine Commonwealth is established with Manuel L. Quezon as president, 
                        marking the transition to independence.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1942-1945</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Japanese Occupation</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        Imperial Japan occupies the Philippines during WWII. The country suffers greatly, 
                        culminating in the bloody Battle of Manila in 1945.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1946</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">Independence Day</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        On July 4, 1946, the United States formally recognizes Philippine independence. 
                        Manuel Roxas becomes the first president of the Third Republic.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1962</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">June 12 Independence</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        President Diosdado Macapagal moves Independence Day to June 12 to commemorate 
                        Aguinaldo's 1898 declaration rather than July 4.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <div class="timeline-date">1986</div>
                    <h3 class="timeline-title">EDSA Revolution</h3>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">
                        The People Power Revolution peacefully overthrows the Marcos regime, restoring 
                        democracy and installing Corazon Aquino as president.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Eras Section -->
    <section class="eras-section" id="eras">
        <div class="section-title">Historical Eras</div>
        <div class="eras-grid">
            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">🏛️</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">Precolonial Period</h3>
                <p class="era-period">Before 1521</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    Ancient kingdoms and barangays thrive with rich trade networks connecting to China, 
                    India, and Southeast Asia. Indigenous cultures develop unique traditions and writing systems.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">⚔️</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">Spanish Colonial Period</h3>
                <p class="era-period">1521-1898</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    333 years of Spanish rule reshape the archipelago. Christianity spreads, new social 
                    structures emerge, and revolutionary movements begin to form against colonial oppression.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">🦅</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">American Period</h3>
                <p class="era-period">1898-1946</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    The Philippines transitions from Spanish to American rule. Public education expands, 
                    infrastructure develops, but the fight for true independence continues.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">🇯🇵</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">Japanese Occupation</h3>
                <p class="era-period">1942-1945</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    WWII brings hardship and resistance. Guerrilla movements fight occupation while 
                    civilians endure the brutal war years, culminating in the liberation of 1945.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">⭐</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">Third Republic</h3>
                <p class="era-period">1946-1972</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    The Philippines enjoys independence and democratic governance, though challenged by 
                    economic development, Huk insurgency, and emerging political dynasties.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="era-card">
                <div class="era-icon">✊</div>
                <h3 class="era-title">Modern Era</h3>
                <p class="era-period">1986-Present</p>
                <p class="era-desc">
                    Post-EDSA Philippines continues to evolve as a democratic nation, facing contemporary 
                    challenges while celebrating its rich cultural heritage and resilient spirit.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Heroes Section -->
    <section class="heroes-section" id="heroes">
        <div class="section-title">National Heroes</div>
        <div class="heroes-grid">
            <div class="hero-card">
                <h3 class="hero-name">José Rizal</h3>
                <p class="hero-role">National Hero</p>
                <p>Writer of "Noli Me Tangere" and "El Filibusterismo" who sparked revolution through his pen.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-card">
                <h3 class="hero-name">Andrés Bonifacio</h3>
                <p class="hero-role">Father of the Revolution</p>
